    <p class="lead">
        Welcome to our Hospital Management System. This Privacy Policy outlines how this system protects the privacy of patients and ensures secure access within our hospital. This system is strictly intended for use by authorized hospital staff, and any access or use by unauthorized individuals is prohibited.
    </p>

